Package: geostatDB
Type: Package
Title: Interface for geostatistical data 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
	person("Falk", "Hesse", email = "falk.hesze@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
	person("Nura", "Kawa", email = "nkawa@berkeley.edu", role = "aut"),
	person("Karina", "Cucchi", email = "karina.cucchi@berkeley.edu", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Falk Hesse <falk.hesze@gmail.com>
Description: The World-Wide Hydrogeological Parameters DAtabase (WWHYPDA) is 
	an online database for the collection of geostatistical data relevant 
	to stochastic hydrogeology. The geostatDB package provides an interface 
	to this database to be used in conjuction with the exPrior package but
	possibly other R packages as well.
Depends:
	R (>= 3.2.2),
	stats,
	DBI,
	RSQLite
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
